	   <tr><td colspan=2>Forget the half-elf and human. The best race for a druid are hafling and wood elf. Forget the half-elf and human.<br><br>They both start with a fair wisdom lvl, and have some nice perk.<br><br>My druid is a hafling, they are less strong&nbsp;&nbsp;then wood elf but they get an inate hidding ability and infravision. Also they have what is maybe the best newbee zone right next to their city. Misty ticket...<br><br>At higher lvl you won't see much difference between hafling and wood elf.<br><br>Hope this help<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Throglogith Bearbugger<br>Druid and lover of the forest<br>Follower of Karana<br>51st cycle of life</td></tr>
