	   <tr><td colspan=2>Let's clear up some things that are being muddied by some people:<br><br>Talking about Wood Elves vs. Halflings, Halflings have HIGHER STR, HIGHER STA, SAME AGI, HIGHER DEX, SAME WIS.&nbsp;&nbsp;They are 8 points stupider than Wood Elves.  They have 25 points LOWER CHA.<br><br>Starting stats:<br><br>--------STR STA AGI DEX WIS INT CHA<br>Half Elf 70, 80, 90, 85, 70, 75, 75<br>Halfling 70, 85, 95, 90, 90, 67, 50<br>Human 75, 85, 75, 75, 85, 75, 75<br>Wood Elf 65, 75, 95, 80, 90, 75, 75<br><br>They all get 30 points to spend at creation.<br><br>Hope that helps.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Nov  7 15:01:57 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
